

lesson 4





    1. Habits and Routines:

I go to school every day.

You eat breakfast at 8.

Nina cleans her room every afternoon.

He goes to work every morning.


        

        point ==>  He , She , It => add "es/s" in the end of verb.



    2. Facts:

Water boils at 100C.

Sun rise in the east.

Earth is circular.



    3. Discribtion:

I am 21.

You have brown eyes.

This apartment has two bedroom.

He has strong skills.






        point==>    we use "has" for He,She,It.











